'''The Castle''' was a large rock formation that was located on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Dorvalla/Legends|Dorvalla]]. This was the location of one of [[Lommite Limited]]'s largest mines of [[Lommite/Legends|lommite]] ore. In [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]], the towering Castle was destroyed by a pair of [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttles]] that had been sabotaged by [[InterGalactic Ore]], who had illicitly acquired the access codes of the shuttles' guidance [[Droid/Legends|droids]].<ref name="Saboteur">[[Darth Maul: Saboteur]]</ref>

